name: [Tier3] Loot Chest!
description:
Welcome to the Loot Chest project!

We have currently just set up 3 Loot Chest for the community to join!
Each Loot Chest collection has different prizes that may be looted!

This Loot Chest consists of 500 prizes!
1 winner will receive a Cool Cats!
1 winner will receive a Tezzardz!
498 winners will receive 5tezos!

And sadly, the remaining loot chests will be empty :(

All you have to do is enter is buy one of these loot chests and wait for your possible prizes when the collection is completed!
Good luck everyone and be sure to check out the two other Loot Chests as well!
Twitter, telegram, and discord will be made public in the next week!
We are super excited and can't wait to see who has the luck to loot a huge chest!
